      "grammarNote": "Pain in Arabic: '[body part] يؤلمني / تؤلمني' (yu'limuni / tu'limuni) = '[body part] hurts me'. يؤلم is for masculine nouns, تؤلم for feminine. Alternatively: 'عندي ألم في [body part]' (indi alam fi...) = I have pain in [body part].",
